":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#6$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":150},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"如果这样的措辞能让您好受些的话，我没意见。","id":151,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#6$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2","focus":"2","id":152},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"白垩的尘世之音是损坏的，罗德岛还发现了那东西的副作用。","id":153,"figure":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#6$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2","focus":"2","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"损坏的尘世之音能除去另一段尘世之音吗？就算能，罗德岛难道会坐视不理？","id":155,"figure":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":156},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"首先，白垩的尘世之音仍然能参与共振。","id":157,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":158},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"至于罗德岛......您以为这是哪里？","id":159,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"这里是维谢海姆，我的领地。","id":161,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":162},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"那位芙蓉小姐又是个感染者，能让她踏入莱塔尼亚境内，已经是给罗德岛面子了。她除了维谢海姆哪儿也去不了。","id":163,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2","focus":"1","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"更何况，她只知道您和白垩会引发一些后果，却完全不知道这后果是怎么来的。她没有任何证据。","id":165,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2","focus":"2","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"......","id":167,"figure":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#2$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2","focus":"1","id":168},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"我知道，您不忍伤害那些与此事毫无瓜葛的感染者。","id":169,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2","focus":"1","id":170},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"在我看来，这是一种不必要的怜悯，但如果您确有此意，就更应该按计划行动了。","id":171,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"2","id":172},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"按计划行动，接着让那些感染者送死？","id":173,"figure":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":174},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"我来告诉您计划的剩余部分吧。","id":175,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":176},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"您和白垩合奏，除去自己的尘世之音。","id":177,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":178},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"然后，我会在音乐厅里引发一定的混乱，您趁乱逃走，我则借机杀死白垩，将他的尸体伪装成您的——","id":179,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2","focus":"2","id":180},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"你说什么？！","id":182,"figure":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#12$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2","focus":"1","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"因为他现在就是夕照区最大的祸害，他不可能不死。","id":184,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#12$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#12$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"2","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"黑键","text":"不可能不死——别想唬我，夕照区最大的祸害难道不是你吗？！","id":186,"figure":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#2$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"我之前已经说了，夕照区的一切灾祸都来源于白垩体内损坏的尘世之音。","id":188,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"共振加剧了尘世之音能量的泄漏，而这是不可逆的。","id":190,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"就算您刚刚真的从移动城市上一跃而下，白垩的尘世之音也不会回到一周前那种接近无害的状态了。","id":192,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"更重要的是，尘世之音不仅在伤害白垩身边的人，也在伤害他自己。","id":194,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#6$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"他才是你们俩共振最大的受害者。","id":196,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":197},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"别看他这段时间好像很健康，但那也只是一种看起来更无害的假愈罢了。","id":198,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"白垩的身体本来已经适应了尘世之音，但最近急剧上升的泄漏强度马上就要让这种危险的平衡崩溃了。","id":200,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"估计得乐观一些，他的好日子大概会在两周后结束，成为假愈期结束后急性症状最为剧烈的那个感染者。","id":202,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":203},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"为了他，也为了夕照区，他最好的下场就是死在合奏之后。","id":204,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#2$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":205},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"这对你，对我，对夕照区，对他自己，都是好事。","id":206,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"我获得了一张随时可以打出的牌，夕照区获得了平静，白垩获得了安宁。","id":208,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#10$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"而您......您将获得自由。","id":210,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#10$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":211},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"乌提卡伯爵，莱塔尼亚的合法继承人......","id":212,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_484_1#2$1","name2":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2","focus":"1","id":213},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"格特鲁德","text":"巫王最后的血脉。","id":214,"figure":"avg_npc_484_1#2$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":215},{"type":"character","id":216},{"type":"stopmusic","id":217},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":218},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.4","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":219},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.6","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":220},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_tinnitus","volume":"1","id":221},{"type":"delay","time":"0.01","id":222},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.3","id":223},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":224},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.8","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":225},{"type":"character","id":226},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$flashback","volume":"0.4","id":227},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":228},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.4","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":229},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.8","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":230},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0.7","fadetime":"0","id":231},{"type":"Background","image":"28_g7_concerthall_outside","screenadapt":"coverall","id":232},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":233},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"$loneliness_loop","volume":"0.4","id":234,"musicid":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":235},{"type":"Text","text":"自由。","id":236},{"type":"Text","text":"自打有记忆以来，我就不曾知晓什么是自由。","id":237},{"type":"dialog","id":238},{"type":"character","id":239},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$flashback","volume":"0.4","id":240},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":241},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.4","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":242},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.8","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":243},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0.7","fadetime":"0","id":244},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ltroom","screenadapt":"coverall","id":245},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_487_1#1$1","blackstart":"0.2","blackend":"0.7","id":246},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":247},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":248},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"可怜的孩子。","id":249,"figure":"avg_npc_487_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不必多礼，也不必问好，只需听我说即可。","id":250,"figure":"avg_npc_487_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"虽然出生在和巫王相距甚远的旁支，但你的确已经是巫王最后的血脉了。","id":251,"figure":"avg_npc_487_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"出于对你个人的怜悯，我不会为难你。","id":252,"figure":"avg_npc_487_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不仅如此，你还将得到你的家族世代相传的封地。","id":253,"figure":"avg_npc_487_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你将成为乌提卡的领主。","id":254,"figure":"avg_npc_487_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你将学会对自己的领民负责。","id":255,"figure":"avg_npc_487_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你将走上一条与你臭名昭著的亲族完全不同的道路——","id":256,"figure":"avg_npc_487_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我这样期待着。","id":257,"figure":"avg_npc_487_1#1$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":258},{"type":"character","id":259},{"type":"Text","text":"这是我记忆的起点。","id":260},{"type":"Text","text":"当时我大概五六岁，之前的事一概记不清，只是模模糊糊地记得，自己好像和一种叫“尘世之音”的怪东西有什么联系，差点没了命。","id":261},{"type":"Text","text":"盯着眼前洁白的裙摆，我当时满心以为，自己会成为一个默默无闻的小贵族。","id":262},{"type":"Text","text":"除了偶尔要忍受尘世之音带来的头痛和幻听之外，我将风平浪静地度过余生。","id":263},{"type":"dialog","id":264},{"type":"character","id":265},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$flashback","volume":"0.4","id":266},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":267},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.4","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":268},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":269},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0.7","fadetime":"0","id":270},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ltroom","screenadapt":"coverall","id":271},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":272},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":273},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面无表情的贵族","text":"伯爵阁下，您应该谨言慎行，不应随意踏出自己的高塔。","id":275,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面无表情的贵族","text":"要知道，您的一切都是女皇陛下赐予的。","id":277,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_243","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"谨小慎微的佣人","text":"伯爵阁下，您是不是忘了什么？","id":279,"figure":"avg_npc_243"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_243","id":280},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"谨小慎微的佣人","text":"在吃饭之前，您应当赞颂女皇陛下之名。","id":281,"figure":"avg_npc_243"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"循规蹈矩的教师","text":"伯爵阁下，今天我们来学一首新曲子。","id":283,"figure":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"循规蹈矩的教师","text":"这首曲子抒发了贵族们对女皇陛下的感激之情，请您牢记在心。","id":285,"figure":"avg_npc_498_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_068","id":286},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"庸庸碌碌的术师","text":"伯爵阁下，您对源石技艺的操控真是高明！","id":287,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"庸庸碌碌的术师","text":"什么，更精细的操作？哈哈，您何必让自己那么累呢。","id":288,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"dialog","id":289},{"type":"character","id":290},{"type":"Text","text":"身边的所有人都在竭力限制我的自由，往我的脑子里面灌输对双子女皇的忠诚。","id":291},{"type":"Text","text":"如果这就是风平浪静的代价，那我可以忍受。","id":292},{"type":"Text","text":"我忍受了很久。","id":293},{"type":"dialog","id":294},{"type":"character","id":295},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$flashback","volume":"0.4","id":296},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":297},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.4","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":298},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":299},{"type":"cameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0.7","fadetime":"0","id":300},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ltroom","screenadapt":"coverall","id":301},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":302},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":303},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1","id":304},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面无表情的贵族","text":"伯爵大人，我开门见山地说吧，您才是莱塔尼亚真正的主人。","id":305,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面无表情的贵族","text":"我已经在您的塔中潜伏了许多年了，想必您也认得我。","id":307,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1","id":308},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面无表情的贵族","text":"不，您不必说话，您听我说，不必赞同也不必驳斥。","id":309,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1","id":310},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面无表情的贵族","text":"我知道，您在畏惧，您不想连现在的生活都失去。但您至少应该知道，那些人究竟怎么看您，想对您做什么。","id":311,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1","id":312},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"面无表情的贵族","text":"您一定知道，僭主强加给您的代理正在下面设宴会客。我将把您带到那里，让您知道真相。","id":313,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":314},{"type":"character","id":315},{"type":"Text","text":"眼前的人拉了我一把，把我从地上拉了起来。","id":316},{"type":"Text","text":"我手里全是汗。","id":317},{"type":"dialog","id":318},{"type":"character","id":319},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$flashback","volume":"0.4","id":320},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":321},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.4","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":322},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":323},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":324},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"coverall","id":325},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":326},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":327},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"狂妄的声音","text":"好酒！","id":328,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"狂妄的声音","text":"地窖里居然有这种佳酿，我可真没想到。","id":329,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"熟悉的声音","text":"您过奖了。","id":330,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"熟悉的声音","text":"乌提卡这穷乡僻壤什么都缺，酿酒的师傅倒是不少。","id":331,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Image","image":"28_i04","fadetime":"2","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","id":332},{"type":"ImageTween","image":"28_i04","xScaleTo":"1.2","yScaleTo":"1.2","duration":"80","id":333},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"狂妄的声音","text":"趁那小子还没长大，咱们可得多喝几桶，不能给他留着！","id":334,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"熟悉的声音","text":"哈哈，这可不行。","id":335,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"熟悉的声音","text":"那小子被软禁在这儿好几年了，我正等着什么时候教他喝酒呢。我得往死里灌他，把他灌成一个彻头彻尾的酒鬼。","id":336,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"background","id":337},{"type":"Text","text":"我一时有点恍惚。","id":338},{"type":"dialog","id":339},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","text":"","id":340},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":341},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"“你将成为乌提卡的领主。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":342},{"type":"subtitle","id":343},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","text":"","id":344},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"狂妄的声音","text":"嗬，原来你还藏着这一手。","id":345,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"狂妄的声音","text":"等那小子彻底泡死在酒里，陛下心里的这颗石头——","id":346,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"熟悉的声音","text":"嘘！","id":347,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"狂妄的声音","text":"对对对，我该死、我该死！我自罚一杯！","id":348,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":349},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","text":"","id":350},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":351},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"“你将学会对自己的领民负责。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":352},{"type":"subtitle","id":353},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","text":"","id":354},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"熟悉的声音","text":"不过，这话只在酒桌上说。","id":355,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"熟悉的声音","text":"绝不能让那小子留下子嗣，这是上头给我的死命令。","id":356,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"狂妄的声音","text":"既然这样，你何不找个药剂师......","id":357,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"熟悉的声音","text":"那可不成，会留下把柄的。只有让他自甘堕落，我这任务才算圆满完成！","id":358,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"狂妄的声音","text":"高！实在是高！来，喝！","id":359,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":360},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","text":"","id":361},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.5","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":362},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"“你将走上一条与你臭名昭著的亲族完全不同的道路。”","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":363},{"type":"subtitle","id":364},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","text":"","id":365},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"熟悉的声音","text":"如果我能平平安安地送走那小子，乌提卡就是我的了。","id":366,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"狂妄的声音","text":"哦哦哦！来，干杯！","id":367,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"熟悉的声音","text":"干杯！","id":368,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":369},{"type":"image","fadetime":"1.5","id":370},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":371},{"type":"dialog","id":372},{"type":"character","id":373},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$flashback","volume":"0.4","id":374},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":375},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.4","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":376},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":377},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凭空出现的声音","text":"哈哈，哈哈哈哈哈哈......","id":378,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凭空出现的声音","text":"小子，听见了吗？","id":379,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"凭空出现的声音","text":"这就是你要的风平浪静的一生！","id":380,"figure":"avg_npc_493_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":381},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":382},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":383},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":384},{"type":"Character","id":385},{"type":"Background",